Name: artillery
Description: Load testing at cloud-scale. Serverless & distributed out-of-the-box. Load test with Playwright. Load test HTTP APIs, GraphQL, WebSocket, and more. Use any Node.js module. Never fail to scale with Artillery!

Packages.Description: Expectations and assertions for HTTP scenarios

Packages.Description: Add fake test data easily to your Artillery test scripts.

Packages.Name: artillery-plugin-memory-inspector
Packages.Description: Inspect the memory of processes running together with your load tests!

Packages.Name: artillery-plugin-metrics-by-endpoint
Packages.Description: Per-endpoint breakdown of latency and response codes for Artillery HTTP tests.

Packages.Description: Publish metrics from your Artillery.io tests to external monitoring & observability systems
